text: William Edmondson (1874–1951) was an African-American sculptor. William Edmondson may also refer to: *William Edmondson (footballer) (played 1902-03), English footballer *William Edmundson (1627–1712), or Edmondson, English founder of Quakerism in Ireland *William B. Edmondson (1927–2013), American army officer *William Edmondson (sound engineer) (1906–1998), American sound engineer
title: William Edmondson (disambiguation)
